Add Filter Logic

Filter logic governs how and when filters apply to your report.

Available in: both Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To create, edit, and delete reports:
Create and Customize Reports
Report Builder

To create custom list views:
Read on the type of record included in the list
Manage Public List Views

Filter logic operators:

OPERATOR	DEFINITION
AND	Finds records that match both values.
OR	Finds records that match either value.
NOT	Finds records that exclude values.

Click Save.

Note: Filter logic isn't available for all filters.
